FT  01 DEC 92 / Parliament and Politics: Council tax details issued today
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE valuations of millions of individual homes for the purposes of the
council tax are available from local authorities from today.
But although householders can find out now which of the eight property bands
on which the tax is based, no appeal against the banding can be made until
next April, when the tax comes into effect.
